Brendan Healy (comedian) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brendan_Healy_(comedian) 0 Brendan Healy (18 December 1956 – 18 February 2016) was a British entertainer from North East England. Beginning as a musician (on keyboards and occasional trombone), he worked in television, becoming an actor, theatre writer and producer, and, later, a comedian.
